{
  "texts": [
    "That your humanity is not considered.",
    "And that they make business out of your lacks.",
    "How could that not upset us.",
    "It upsets us and puts us in a position of class struggle between those who have the power and are squeezing us, and those of us who are right but that do not have that economic power.",
    "The above quotation criticises how profit-seeking can prevail over the well-being of the Cerrillos residents."
  ]
}